Title: Dew Drop Serum — UGC Spot
Author: wavelet-director

INT. BATHROOM VANITY - MORNING

ALEX, late twenties, freckles, glossy brunette hair, leans toward the mirror holding her phone like she's just remembered something. Soft window light. She turns to camera, half-laughing.

ALEX
Okay I have to tell you about this.

CUT TO:

INT. APARTMENT WINDOW - CONTINUOUS

ALEX in the same cream ribbed tank, holds a small clear glass serum bottle next to her cheek. Window light overexposes her highlights slightly.

ALEX
Two drops, morning and night.

CUT TO:

INT. APARTMENT WINDOW - CONTINUOUS

ECU on ALEX's hands. She tilts the clear glass bottle. A single bead forms on the black pipette tip, catches the window light, hangs.

CUT TO:

INT. BATHROOM VANITY - MORNING

ALEX back at the vanity, shrugs, grins wide at the camera, almost embarrassed.

ALEX
My skin has never looked like this.

FADE OUT.
